CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: SeqLL Inc is a life science instrumentation and services company. Its True Single Molecule Sequencing platform offers a single molecule solution for DNA and RNA sequencing by performing the detection of nucleic acids. The data produced by the platform generates molecular profiles, providing researchers with new insights into biology.
